invariant concurrent_futures_extra111.Future_done_coqualname_len_11:
  description: "concurrent.futures.Future.done.__code__.co_qualname.__len__() == 11 — 'Future.done' = 'Future.'=7 + 'done'=4 = 11; this is the shortest co_qualname in this spec; concurrent.futures.Future.done.__code__.co_qualname.__eq__('Future.done')==True; concurrent.futures.Future.done.__code__.co_argcount==1 (self only — done() returns True if the future is done, regardless of success or cancellation); concurrent.futures.Future.done.__code__.co_name=='done' (len=4, the shortest method name among all Future methods); co_qualname length ordering: done=11 (shortest) < cancel=result=13 < running=14 < __init__=15 < cancelled=exception=16 < set_result=17 < set_exception=20 < add_done_callback=24 (longest); NEW in extra111: first standalone Future.done co_qualname length invariant in cfcoq111 namespace; wave 255; verified with Python 3.14.3"
  category: code_attrs
  kind: python_call_eq
  function: concurrent.futures.Future.done.__code__.co_qualname.__len__
