invariant concurrent_futures_extra111.Future_running_coqualname_len_14:
  description: "concurrent.futures.Future.running.__code__.co_qualname.__len__() == 14 — 'Future.running' = 'Future.'=7 + 'running'=7 = 14; concurrent.futures.Future.running.__code__.co_qualname.__eq__('Future.running')==True; concurrent.futures.Future.running.__code__.co_argcount==1 (self only — running() returns True when the future is currently being executed by an executor, i.e., not yet done and not cancelled); concurrent.futures.Future.running.__code__.co_name=='running' (len=7); compare: 'running'=7 chars (method name) and 'Future.'=7 chars (prefix) give total co_qualname len=14 = 7+7; co_qualname length ordering: done=11 < cancel=result=13 < running=14 < __init__=15 < ...; type(concurrent.futures.Future.running).__name__=='function' (Python-defined); NEW in extra111: first standalone Future.running co_qualname length invariant in cfcoq111 namespace; wave 255; verified with Python 3.14.3"
  category: code_attrs
